  "prompt": "Why haven't we seen Jack Nicholson in any film lately?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, Jack Nicholson has been relatively absent from film since his last major role in \"How Do You Know\" (2010). There are a few possible reasons for his absence:\n\n1. **Retirement**: It's widely rumored that Nicholson has retired from acting, citing health issues, including memory loss, which have made it difficult for him to perform.\n\n2. **Personal Preference**: After such a prolific career, he may simply choose to step back and enjoy his life away from the spotlight.\n\n3. **Legacy and Impact**: Nicholson has an extensive body of work and might feel that he has already contributed significantly to cinema.\n\nWhile he may still be involved in Hollywood in some capacity, his focus seems to have shifted away from acting in recent years.",
